OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FVideo Report by Rob Smith
OL,8,FThe Archbishop of Liverpool Malcolm
OL,9,FMcMahon OP, has declared the sudden
OL,10,Frecovery of a man from Merseyside with
OL,11,Fepilepsy was a miracle.
OL,13,FJohn (Jack) Traynor was a pilgrim on
OL,14,Fthe archdiocese's first official
OL,15,Fpilgrimage to Lourdes in 1923, he was
OL,16,Fcured of epilepsy, paralysis of the
OL,17,Fright arm and paraplegia during the
OL,18,Fpilgrimage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
