OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FThe case is believed to be miraculous
OL,7,Fby people across the archdiocese and
OL,8,Fbeyond, but, despite an attempt in
OL,9,F1993, there has never been an official
OL,10,Fecclesiastical declaration until
OL,11,FSunday 8 December.
OL,13,FIt is the 71st official miracle to
OL,14,Fhave happened in Lourdes and the first
OL,15,Fperson from England to be recognised.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
