OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FIn 2023, Dr Kieran Moriarty, an
OL,7,FEnglish member of the International
OL,8,FMedical Committee of Lourdes, was
OL,9,Fasked to conduct a review of the file
OL,10,Fof John Traynor held in the archives
OL,11,Fat Lourdes.
OL,13,FDr Moriarty unearthed a reference in
OL,14,Fthe file to a report by Dr Vallet, the
OL,15,Fthen Acting President of the BdCM.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
