OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FHis report, which was published in
OL,7,FFrench, appears never to have been
OL,8,Fsent to Liverpool, and indeed no
OL,9,Fpotential miraculous cures were ever
OL,10,Freferred from Lourdes to diocesan
OL,11,Fbishops between 1913 and 1946.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
