OL,3,CMan's recovery in 1923 declared first
OL,4,CEnglish miracle
OL,6,FArchbishop Malcolm said: "Given the
OL,7,Fweight of medical evidence, the
OL,8,Ftestimony to the faith of John Traynor
OL,9,Fand his devotion to Our Blessed Lady,
OL,10,Fit is with great joy that I declare
OL,11,Fthat the cure of John Traynor, from
OL,12,Fmultiple serious medical conditions,
OL,13,Fis to be recognised as a miracle
OL,14,Fwrought by the power of God through
OL,15,Fthe intercession of Our Lady of
OL,16,FLourdes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
